data.description: Nice waterfront home with a 70 foot long concrete dock/bulkhead. Located on a navigable canal that feeds into the Amite River. Waterfront living without the flooding. This is a non--flood zone and has not flooded. The home consists of 3 bedrooms and two baths. Very open and airy floorplan with a huge sunroom looking over the dock area. Kitchen features white cabinets and granite counters. This is a Bankruptcy Court ordered sale.
